{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DOMTokenList","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/length\"><code>length</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/value\"><code>value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/add\"><code>add()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/contains\"><code>contains()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/forEach\"><code>forEach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/item\"><code>item()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/keys\"><code>keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/remove\"><code>remove()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/replace\"><code>replace()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/supports\"><code>supports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/toggle\"><code>toggle()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/values\"><code>values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>DOMTokenList</strong></code>&nbsp;接口表示一组空格分隔的标记（tokens）。如由 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/classList\"><code>Element.classList</code></a>、<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLinkElement/relList\"><code>HTMLLinkElement.relList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>、<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLAnchorElement/relList\"><code>HTMLAnchorElement.relList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 或 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLAreaElement/relList\"><code>HTMLAreaElement.relList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 返回的一组值。它和&nbsp;JavaScript <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a> 对象一样，索引从 0 开始。<code>DOMTokenList</code>&nbsp;总是区分大小写（case-sensitive）。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.length\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/length\"><code>DOMTokenList.length</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>一个整数，表示存储在该对象里值的个数。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/value\"><code>DOMTokenList.value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>该属性以 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 的形式返回 <strong><code>DOMTokenList</code>&nbsp;</strong>列表的值。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.itemindex\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/item\" title=\"DOMTokenList.item(<var>index</var>)\"><code>DOMTokenList.item(<var>index</var>)</code></a></dt>\n <dd>根据传入的索引值返回一个值，如果索引值大于等于符号列表的长度（<code>length</code>），则返回 <code>undefined</code> 或 <code>null</code>，在 <span title=\"(Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4)\">Gecko&nbsp;7.0</span> 之前的版本中返回 <code>null</code>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.containstoken\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/contains\" title=\"DOMTokenList.contains(<var>token</var>)\"><code>DOMTokenList.contains(<var>token</var>)</code></a></dt>\n <dd>如果 DOMTokenList 列表中包括相应的字符串 <code>token</code>，则返回&nbsp;<code>true</code>，否则返回&nbsp;<code>false</code>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.addtoken1_token2_...tokenn\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/add\" title=\"DOMTokenList.add(<var>token1</var>[,&nbsp;<var>token2</var>[, ...<var>tokenN</var>]])\"><code>DOMTokenList.add(<var>token1</var>[,&nbsp;<var>token2</var>[, ...<var>tokenN</var>]])</code></a></dt>\n <dd>添加一个或多个标记（<code>token</code>）到 <code>DOMTokenList</code> 列表中。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.removetoken1_token2_...tokenn\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/remove\" title=\"DOMTokenList.remove(<var>token1</var>[,&nbsp;<var>token2</var>[, ...<var>tokenN</var>]])\"><code>DOMTokenList.remove(<var>token1</var>[,&nbsp;<var>token2</var>[, ...<var>tokenN</var>]])</code></a></dt>\n <dd>从 <code>DOMTokenList</code> 列表中移除一个或多个标记（<code>token</code>）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.replaceoldtoken_newtoken\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/replace\" title=\"DOMTokenList.replace(<var>oldToken</var>,&nbsp;<var>newToken</var>)\"><code>DOMTokenList.replace(<var>oldToken</var>,&nbsp;<var>newToken</var>)</code></a></dt>\n <dd>使用&nbsp;<code><var>newToken</var></code>&nbsp;替换&nbsp;<code><var>token</var></code><var>&nbsp;。</var></dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.supportstoken_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/supports\"><code>DOMTokenList.supports(<var>token</var>)</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>如果传入的&nbsp;<code><var>token</var></code>&nbsp;是相关属性（attribute）支持的标记，则返回 <code>true</code>&nbsp;。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.toggletoken_force\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/toggle\" title=\"DOMTokenList.toggle(<var>token</var>&nbsp;[,&nbsp;<var>force</var>])\"><code>DOMTokenList.toggle(<var>token</var>&nbsp;[,&nbsp;<var>force</var>])</code></a></dt>\n <dd>从 DOMTokenList 字符串中移除标记字串（<code><em>token</em></code>），并返回 <code>false</code>。如果传入的字串（<code><em>token</em></code>）不存在，则将其添加进去，并返回 <code>true</code>&nbsp;。<code><em>force</em></code><em>&nbsp;</em>是一个可选的布尔值，如果传入 <code>true</code>&nbsp;，且传入的&nbsp;<em><code>token</code>&nbsp;</em>不存在，则将其添加进去并返回&nbsp;<code>true</code>&nbsp;，若传入的&nbsp;<em><code>token</code>&nbsp;</em>存在，则直接返回 <code>true</code>&nbsp;；反之，如果传入&nbsp;<code>false</code>&nbsp;，则移除存在的&nbsp;<code><em>token</em></code><em>&nbsp;，</em>并返回&nbsp;<code>false</code>&nbsp;，如&nbsp;<code><em>token</em></code>&nbsp;不存在则直接返回&nbsp;<code>false</code>&nbsp;。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.entries_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/entries\"><code>DOMTokenList.entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>返回一个迭代器（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a>），以遍历这个对象中的所有键值对。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.foreachcallback_thisarg_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/forEach\"><code>DOMTokenList.forEach(<var>callback</var>&nbsp;[,&nbsp;<var>thisArg</var>])</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>为每个 <code>DOMTokenList</code>&nbsp;中的元素都调用一次传入的 <code><var>callback</var></code><var>&nbsp;</var>函数&nbsp;。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.keys\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/keys\"><code>DOMTokenList.keys()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>返回一个迭代器（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a>）以遍历这个对象中所有键值对的键。</dd>\n <dt id=\"domtokenlist.values_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/values\"><code>DOMTokenList.values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>返回一个迭代器（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a>）以遍历这个对象中所有键值对的值。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在下面这个简单的例子中，我们使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/classList\"><code>Element.classList</code></a> 获取了 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> 元素的 class 列表，也就是一个<code>DOMTokenList</code>&nbsp;，再使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/add\"><code>DOMTokenList.add()</code></a> 添加了一个 class，然后更新 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code>&nbsp;元素的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>Node.textContent</code></a>以显示这个新的 <code>DOMTokenList</code>。</p>\n\n<p>HTML:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p class=\"a b c\"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</pre>\n\n<p>JavaScript:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">let para = document.querySelector(\"p\");\nlet classes = para.classList;\npara.classList.add(\"d\");\npara.textContent = `paragraph classList is \"${classes}\"`;</pre>\n\n<p>输出类似这样：</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Examples sample\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"去除空格和重复项目","title":"去除空格和重复项目","isH3":false,"content":"<p>修改&nbsp;<code>DOMTokenList</code>&nbsp;的方法（例如 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/add\"><code>DOMTokenList.add()</code></a>）会自动去除多余的空格（<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Whitespace\">Whitespace <small>(en-US)</small></a>）和列表中的重复项目。例如：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;span class=\"    d   d e f\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</pre>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">let span = document.querySelector(\"span\");\nlet classes = span.classList;\nspan.classList.add(\"x\");\nspan.textContent = `span classList is \"${classes}\"`;</pre>\n\n<p>输出类似这样：</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Trimming of whitespace and removal of duplicates sample\" id=\"frame_trimming_of_whitespace_and_removal_of_duplicates\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/_sample_.trimming_of_whitespace_and_removal_of_duplicates.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect1\"></dt>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\"><strong>规范</strong></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\"><strong>状态</strong></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\"><strong>注释</strong></th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-domtokenlist\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">DOMTokenList</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DOMTokenList","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>DOMSettableTokenList</code></a> (object that extends DOMTokenList with settable <em>.value</em> property)</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=501257\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;501257</a> - Implement HTML 5's HTMLElement.classList property</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"去除空格和重复项目","id":"去除空格和重复项目"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"DOMTokenList 接口表示一组空格分隔的标记（tokens）。如由 Element.classList、HTMLLinkElement.relList (en-US)、HTMLAnchorElement.relList (en-US) 或 HTMLAreaElement.relList (en-US) 返回的一组值。它和 JavaScript Array 对象一样，索引从 0 开始。DOMTokenList 总是区分大小写（case-sensitive）。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DOMTokenList","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"DOMTokenList","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DOMTokenList","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DOMTokenList","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DOMTokenList","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"DOMTokenList","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"DOMTokenList","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/domtokenlist","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/domtokenlist/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList","title":"DOMTokenList"}],"pageTitle":"DOMTokenList - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}